1112
01:22:33,267 --> 01:22:34,894
Maybe this is the only way,

1113
01:22:35,536 --> 01:22:37,197
you'll remember me forever.

1114
01:22:37,772 --> 01:22:39,467
Love, Mandy.

1115
01:22:39,874 --> 01:22:41,239
Mandy did write this.

1116
01:24:00,554 --> 01:24:01,350
You're back?

1117
01:24:04,058 --> 01:24:04,786
