1124
01:24:45,866 --> 01:24:48,198
If the girl they lie to is worth it.

1125
01:24:48,369 --> 01:24:49,961
When you've heard enough, then split.

1126
01:24:50,437 --> 01:24:51,529
My Darling...

1127
01:24:52,873 --> 01:24:53,805
I love you.

1128
01:24:55,142 --> 01:24:56,473
She might remember

1129
01:24:56,944 --> 01:24:58,468
